{"tid":332360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"仲賭緊馬會（足球）既入黎講兩句","createTime":"2017-07-23T02:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:54:29.000Z","uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14f3388d65afa3f98d35ebc0c10bebfe3726f69b","tid":332360,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"足智彩都出左十幾年<br />\n仲玩緊既你 咁多年贏緊定輸緊？<br />\n四五年前已經開始無玩 <br />\n賭波輸多 你可以話我唔識睇盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波多數夜晚踢 極度影響睡眠質素<br />\n訓到一半 又諗有冇買到波 又去睇賽果<br />\n輸撚埋 訓到訓唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以轉左去澳門賭同買正股算 <br />\n個本係大d 勝在唔會影響睡眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a397c42e1d9d66b34a3d155fbfc3e03fbd68deb","tid":332360,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"會影響睡眠即是你未識賭"},{"pid":"3a47961ec5d096a5363c835132aa5b2e72672e5d","tid":332360,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會影響睡眠即是你未識賭</blockquote><br />\n所以咪轉左買股票 賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc510497fe08d6b6d6bce16b53455532cc657c3","tid":332360,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會影響睡眠即是你未識賭</blockquote><br />\n所以咪轉左買股票 賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賭場有種魔力，贏左又想繼續，輸又想繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難走到"},{"pid":"ce2e68d00fce310d57c4f3962c18a8960d268156","tid":332360,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"有咩股票number 推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"